commit.message:
Drop support for Python 2.6, 3.3, 3.4 (#450)

* Drop support for Python 2.6 and 3.3

* upgrade pytest

* Drop support for Python 3.4

* upgrade dev requirements

* drop Python 2.6 support from install_requirements script

* only compare first two version numbers with equals

* add support for python 3.7 to tox

* move mock into py2 requirements

* pep8 is now pycodestyle

* remove install requirements script

* conditionally install travis pip requirements

* pytest 5.0 dropped python2 support

* no longer need werkzeug support for python 3.4

* fix pep8 E741

* advertise support for Python 3.7

* remove py2 requirements file
